Message output:

Messages belong to categories.  These are defined in "trace.h" as an enum.  The
first parameter to __shmem_trace() is one of these values.

All categories are disabled initially, except for "FATAL".

To add a category:

1. add a value to the enum in "trace.h".  Suggest appending to the list.

2. add a table entry to tracers[] in trace.c.  The value is OFF/ON

3. use it
